        "Key": 19,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卡罗琳",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "哎？！有，有这回事吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 20,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "似乎是想在我面前掩盖住自己的疲态，她故意提高了音量。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 21,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我无奈地笑了笑，随后又伸手帮她捋了捋那略显凌乱的刘海。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 22,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卡罗琳",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "分析员的手……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 23,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 6,
        "Speaker": "卡罗琳",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "啊，我的刘海！",
        "disable": 0
    },
